### DrCal API - Testes de Profissionais
### Este arquivo contém exemplos de requisições para testar as rotas de profissionais

### 1. Criar um novo profissional
POST http://localhost:3000/professionals
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "name": "Dr. João Silva",
  "specialty": "Cardiologia",
  "slug": "dr-joao-silva",
  "crm": "12345-SP",
  "rqe": "67890",
  "img_url": "https://example.com/photo.jpg"
}

### 2. Listar todos os profissionais do usuário
GET http://localhost:3000/professionals
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

### 3. Buscar profissional por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

### 4. Buscar profissional por slug (privado)
GET http://localhost:3000/professionals/slug/dr-joao-silva
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

### 5. Buscar profissional por slug (público)
GET http://localhost:3000/professionals/public/dr-joao-silva

### 6. Atualizar profissional
PUT http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "name": "Dr. João Silva Santos",
  "specialty": "Cardiologia Intervencionista",
  "crm": "12345-SP",
  "rqe": "67890"
}

### 7. Excluir profissional (soft delete)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/professionals/{{PROFESSIONAL_ID}}
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

### 8. Teste de validação - Slug inválido
POST http://localhost:3000/professionals
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "name": "Dr. Maria Santos",
  "specialty": "Dermatologia",
  "slug": "dr-maria-santos!@#",
  "crm": "54321-SP"
}

### 9. Teste de validação - Campos obrigatórios faltando
POST http://localhost:3000/professionals
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "specialty": "Ortopedia",
  "crm": "98765-SP"
}

### 10. Teste de validação - ID inválido
GET http://localhost:3000/professionals/invalid-uuid
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

### 11. Teste de slug duplicado
POST http://localhost:3000/professionals
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "name": "Dr. Pedro Costa",
  "specialty": "Neurologia",
  "slug": "dr-joao-silva",
  "crm": "11111-SP"
}

### 12. Teste sem autenticação
GET http://localhost:3000/professionals

### 13. Teste com API key inválida
GET http://localhost:3000/professionals
x-api-key: invalid-api-key

### Variáveis para testes:
# API_KEY: Sua API key válida
# PROFESSIONAL_ID: ID de um profissional criado 